## lyrebird configuration
# Intentionally exclude legacy lyrebird transports: obfs2, obfs3, and scramblesuit
# are deprecated and superseded by obfs4; meek_lite is not exposed because this
# bundle no longer ships the legacy meek-client used by older torrc configs.
ClientTransportPlugin obfs4,webtunnel exec pluggable_transports\lyrebird.exe
ClientTransportPlugin snowflake exec pluggable_transports\lyrebird.exe

## conjure configuration
ClientTransportPlugin conjure exec pluggable_transports\conjure-client.exe -registerURL https://registration.refraction.network/api
